dialog.body: Hello, thank you for contacting Old Stone Auto Insurance. My name is Scott Young. May I have your name, please?
Hi, my name is Madison Smith.
Nice to meet you, Madison. Can you please provide me with your policy number for identification purposes?
Sure, my policy number is eight seven three two one.
Thank you, Madison. One more piece of information needed for security verification. Can you confirm your date of birth, please?
My date of birth is the eleventh of March nineteen eighty-five.
Great, thank you for the information. How can I assist you today, Madison?
I would like to add a new vehicle to my policy.
Of course, I can help you with that. Please provide me with the make, model, and year of the vehicle.
Thank you for your time, Madison. Is there anything else I can assist you with today?
